E. coli MG1655

# Print the conditions where the OD surpassed 0.25 at some point (with other words, where the strains grew)
MG1655 |>
  filter(OD >= .25) |>
  distinct(mol_ID, mol_conc)
##   mol_ID mol_conc
## 1   None        0
## 2     LA       20
## 3   3-HP       20
